comment: /**  * Checks name and aliases of the given bean for URLs, starting with "/".  */
code: /**  * Checks name and aliases of the given bean for URLs, starting with "/".  */ @Override protected String[] determineUrlsForHandler(String beanName) {     List<String> urls = new ArrayList<>().     if (beanName.startsWith("/")) {         urls.add(beanName).     }     String[] aliases = obtainApplicationContext().getAliases(beanName).     for (String alias : aliases) {         if (alias.startsWith("/")) {             urls.add(alias).         }     }     return StringUtils.toStringArray(urls). }
